riCare 第二代口罩型空氣清淨機共推出白、黑兩色，定價 NT$6,990，即日於 LG 官方線上商城、百貨、實體店面等通路開始販售。]]></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Aug 2021 19:00:53 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://hk.news.yahoo.com/lg-%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%B0%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3-puricare-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B8%85%E6%B7%A8%E6%A9%9F-110053174.html</guid><link>https://hk.news.yahoo.com/lg-%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%B0%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3-puricare-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B8%85%E6%B7%A8%E6%A9%9F-110053174.html</link><content:encoded><![CDATA[https://media.zenfs.com/en/engadget_hk_378/e5049b0470e14167e463e52f2f31ad58]]></content:encoded></item></channel></rss>